item.title: Different Kind of Sex Education for a Child
item.description: This is episode 5 in my spin-off from my long-running 'pedo ring' series, which featured a rugged and fairly good-looking pedo called Sean as the central male character. Now, he has had to start all over again. The first paragraph of each episode summarizes what's gone on before, so can be enjoyed separately. Here is the index so far: #1 Ravenous Pedo, Available Little Girl, #2 8yo Simone Learns More, #3 A Master Child-Abuser at Work, #4 The Usefulness of a Little Girl's Mouth.
